{"word":"ἀσφαλῶς","slug":"ἀσφαλῶς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀσφαλῶς</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀσφαλής\">ἀσφαλής</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> ‘in a manner that is certain’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> <i>securely</i> <a href='B:480 14:44'>Mk 14:44</a></b> (<el>ἀ.</el> = <i>under guard)</i>; of a jailer instructed to take strong secure measures <b><a href='B:510 16:23'>Ac 16:23</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> <i>beyond all doubt, for sure</i> <a href='B:510 2:36'>2:36</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀσφαλίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀσχημονέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}